text: Fellen is a community in Main-Spessart in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Burgsinn. ==Geography== ===Location=== Fellen is in the Mittelgebirge Spessart, in the WÃ¼rzburg Region. ===Subdivisions=== The community has the following Gemarkungen (traditional rural cadastral areas): Fellen, Rengersbrunn, Wohnrod and Neuhof. ==References== ==Other websites== * Fellen as part of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft of Burgsinn Category:Main-Spessart
